.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
Choose how kitty draws a window while a resize is in progress. A value of
\fBstatic\fP means draw the current window contents, mostly unchanged. A value
of \fBscale\fP means draw the current window contents scaled. A value of
\fBblank\fP means draw a blank window. A value of \fBsize\fP means show the
window size in cells.
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
